    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A signature Kanigakure grappling strike that exploits your opponent's balance. You make a single melee attack (unarmed or armed). On a hit, the attack deals damage as normal, and you immediately attempt a bull rush against the target as a free action. The target may make a Reflex save to resist being knocked prone if the bull rush succeeds; a successful save prevents the prone condition but does not stop the knockback movement.</p>\n\n",
